  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SensorController
    SensorController provides sensor management for a Sensor Enabled Device (SED).

    SensorCalibrationConfig
    The class defining sensor calibration information as it comes from the device.
    SensorCalibrationConfig.Builder  
    SensorCalibrationConfigRequest
    This class defines a data structure to be sent to the wearable to perform a specific sensor calibration It is very similar to SensorCalibrationConfig which serves for calibration info received from the wearable.

    A simple util class to convert app data structures for sensor calibration to those utilized by the wearable
